{"type": "article", "id": 12177, "title": "Jo Malone London 沐浴系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061356058cmd6FlQJizKU54q.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tJo Malone London 最近推出品牌第一支身体磨砂膏和沐浴油，磨砂膏采用的是天竺葵与天然核桃外壳颗粒，粒子温柔幼滑，不会让身体感到不适。而沐浴油有三种味道，分别是牡丹与胭红麂绒，青柠、罗勒与柑橘，葵花籽、荷荷巴籽油与椰子油。<a href=\"http://www.jomalone.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140016tabiAWjmurgvpwlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614001676pyVbJgsQuM3cSF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140017yjIfls97RprNJhuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140017LYycUMFCoKis2vVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59252336\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}